OL,5, A man who abducted a primary school    
OL,6, girl while dressed as a woman and then 
OL,7, sexually assaulted her in his Borders  
OL,8, home has been jailed for 20 years.     
OL,10,FAndrew Miller, who is also known as Amy
OL,11,FGeorge, offered to give the girl a lift
OL,12,Fhome in February this year.            
OL,14,FBut Miller, 53, instead drove her to   
OL,15,Fhis own house, took her into a bedroom 
OL,16,Fand refused to let her leave.          
OL,18,FHe then subjected her to a series of   
OL,19,Fsexual assaults over the course of the 
OL,20,Fnext 27 hours.                         
